            "title": "全日收市︱午後再回 恒指跌140點報25752點 重磅科股領跌 新興科股逆市揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後反覆向下，尤幸未失守早市低位，「ATMXJ」等科磅科股幾乎全線報跌，新興的AI應用類科股則逆市再升，迅策(03317)便不斷破頂。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"迅策招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"迅策招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">迅策招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早低開136點，初段跌幅曾擴大至239點，見25653點即現反彈，早市中段最高曾見25852點，僅跌40點，其後進入在25750點之上反覆調整階段，午後一度升越早市高位，最高報25854點，跌38點，但後段跌幅再度擴大至過百點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報25752點，跌140點或0.54%。恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，收跌101點或2.06%，報4821點；國企指數跌65點或0.75%，報8611點。主板成交縮減至2449.77億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15852447-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c140%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125752%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 16:18:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股收跌  滬股午後再下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股收跌，滬股午後擴大，兩市成交合計21340.47億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日收報3966，跌28點或0.72%，今早以3967點開市，跌27點或0.69%，上午見3979，跌16點或0.4%，為全日高位，午後進一步下挫，低見3955，跌40點或1%，為全日低位，全日成交9024.82億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日收報13996，跌46點或0.33%，今早開市報13928點，亦跌114點或0.81%，最低見13891，挫151點或1.08%，為全日低位，上午中段見14058，升16點或0.11%，為全日高位，午後窄幅，全日成交12315.65億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日跌29點或0.64%，報4566點 ; 創業板指數全日報3323，跌24點或0.73%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15852037-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e4%b8%8b%e6%bb%91",
